@MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5298

### 1. Register User
POST {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Vincent",
  "email": "vincent@art.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login User
POST {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vincent@art.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Variable: Set Token (Copy from response above if needed for future authenticated requests)
@AuthToken = 

### 3. Create a User (Legacy/Admin - Optional)
POST {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "VincentLegacy",
  "email": "vincent_legacy@art.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Variable: Set User Id (Copy from response above)
@UserId = 81FB461A-C712-42D2-A687-4C46BAE3042E

### 2. Create a Drawing (Canvas)
POST {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/drawings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{UserId}}",
  "title": "Starry Night",
  "width": 1920,
  "height": 1080,
  "isPublic": true
}

### Variable: Set Drawing Id (Copy from response above)
@DrawingId = 42fa3314-3a77-4c60-8835-d203d9022e28

### 3. Add a Background Layer (Fill)
POST {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/drawings/{{DrawingId}}/layers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 0,
  "orderIndex": 0,
  "isVisible": true,
  "isLocked": true,
  "content": "{\"color\": \"#000033\", \"type\": \"fill\"}",
  "configurationJson": "{\"opacity\": 1.0}"
}

### 4. Add a Stroke Layer (Stars)
POST {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/drawings/{{DrawingId}}/layers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 0,
  "orderIndex": 1,
  "isVisible": true,
  "isLocked": false,
  "content": "{\"points\": [[10,10], [20,20], [30,15]], \"color\": \"#FFFF00\", \"width\": 5}",
  "configurationJson": "{\"opacity\": 0.8, \"blendMode\": \"Screen\"}"
}

### 5. Get the Full Drawing
GET {{MagicDraw.Api_HostAddress}}/api/drawings/{{DrawingId}}
Accept: application/json
